On the Origin of Species, published on 24 November 1859, is a kaary of vaigyanik sahitya by charles darwin jisase is mana to be the nyaas of evolutionary biology.
Its full title was On the Origin of Species by Means of prakritik chayan, or the sangrakshan of favoured daud in the sangharsh for Life.
For the chathe sanskaran of 1872, the choti sheershak was changed to The Origin of Species.
Darwin 's book introduced the scientific theory ki populations evolve over the course of peedhiyaan through a prakram of prakritik chayan.
It presented a body of evidence that the diversity of life arose by aam descent through a branching pattern of evolution.
Darwin included evidence that he had gathered on the Beagle expedition in the 1830s or uske subsequent nishkarshon isse shodh, patrachaar, and experimentation.
Various evolutionary vichaar tha already maharoom prastaavit to bataaiye new findings in biology.
There was growing support for such ideas among dissident anatomists and the general public, but dauraan the pehla half of the 19th sadi the angrezi vaigyanik sthapana thi closely tied to the girijaghar of england, while science was part of natural theology.
Ideas about the transmutation of species were controversial as they conflicted with the manyataon ki prajati yahood aparivartansheel bhaag of a designed padanukram or that humans were unique, unrelated to other animals.
the rajnatik or theological implications yahood padati debated, lakin transmutation thi not accepted by the scientific mainstream.
The book was written for non-specialist readers and aakarshith faili byaaj upon iske prakaashan.
As Darwin thi an pratishthit vaigyanik, uske nishkarshon yahood liya seriously or the pramaan he prastut utpann vaigyanik, philosophical, and religious discussion.
The bahes over the kitaab contributed to the abhiyaan by t.h. haxle or uske fellow members of the X Club to secularise science by promoting scientific naturalism.
Within two decades there was widespread vaigyanik anubandh ki evolution, saath a branching pattern of aam descent, tha occurred, lakin vaigyanikon yahood slow to de natural selection the significance that Darwin thought appropriate.
During the `` grahan of darvinavaad `` isse the 1880s to the 1930s, vibhinn other mechanisms of evolution were given more credit.
With the development of the modern evolutionary synthesis in the 1930s and 1940s, Darwin 's concept of evolutionary adaptation through natural selection became central to aadhunik vikasvaadi siddhanth, abhi the unifying avadharana of the jivan sciences.
charles dilan `` kasee '' stangal ( ; july 30, 1890 – sitambar 29, 1975 ), nicknamed `` the boodha perfessor '', thi an American Major League Baseball outfielder and manager.
He thi nirvaachit to the besabaal Hall of Fame in.
Stengel was born in Kansas City, mizori, or originally nicknamed `` dach '', a aam upnaam at ki time for Americans of German ancestry.

In the 1950s, sportswriters utaavle use saath yet another upnaam, `` the boodha praadhyaapak '' ( or `` Perfessor '' ), for his sharp wit and his ability to talk at length on anything baseball -related.
haalanki uske besabaal kariyar spanned a kramank of tiimon or cities, he is primarily associated with clubs in New York City.
Between playing and managing, he is the tabhi man to have worn chaar of nai york 's pramukh lig club ' uniforms.
He was the pehla of chaar main ( through the ritu ) to manage dono the nai york yankis or nai york mets ; yogi Berra, Dallas Green, and Joe Torre are the others.
Like Torre, he bhi prabandhit the Braves and the Dodgers.
He ended his baseball career as the beloved manager for the then vistaar nai york mets, jisase jiti over the dil of nai york partly due to the adwitiya akshar of unke diggaj netaa.
June ( ) is the sixth month of the saal in the julian or gregorian panchang or ek of the four months with a length of 30 days.
Ovid provides two etymologies for June 's name in his kavita concerning the maheene hakdaar the Fasti.
The pehla is ki the maah is namit baad the roman devi juno, bivi of brihaspati or samatuly to the Greek goddess Hera ; the second is that the name comes from the Latin word iuniores, meaning `` younger ones, '' as opposed to maiores ( `` elders '' ) for which the preceding month May may be named ( Fasti VI.1–88 ).
See : Months in various calendars also called the season of the June is the month with the longest daylight ghanton of the saal in the uttari golardh or the shortest daylight ghanton of the saal in the dakshini golardh.
June in the uttari golardh is the mausami samatuly to disambar in the dakshini golardh and vice versa.
in the uttari golardh, the shuruuaat of the meteorological summer is 1 June.
In the Southern golardh, the shuruuaat of the meteorological sheet is 1 June.
At the start of June, the sun rises in the nakshatra of vrish ; at the samaapt of june, the surya udai in the constellation of Gemini.
however, due to the precession of the equinoxes, june begins saath the surya in the astrological chihn of Gemini, and ends with the sun in the astrological sign of Cancer.
June is known for the large kramank of vivaah ki occur over the course of the maah.
According to one etymology, june is namit baad Juno ( Hera ).
Juno was the devi of vivaah or a shaadishuda yugal 's household, so some consider it good luck to be married in this month.
According to another etymology provided by the roman kavi ovid, june is namit liye the iuniores, latin liye `` yang logon '' ( fasti vi.88 ) or ki the month of May is named for the maiores, Latin for `` elders ''.
In Iceland, loakgeet says ki if tum bathe nagn in the morning os on the morning of june 24, you are supposed to keep aging at bay for longer.
a samvidhan is a niyat of aadharbhoot siddhanth or sthapit precedents according to which a state or other organization is governed.
These rules saath mek up, i.e. constitute, kayaa the entity is.
When these principles are likhaa bas into a single dastauez or niyat of vidhik dastauez, those dastauez may be kaha to embody a likhaa samvidhan ; if ve hai likhaa down in a single comprehensive document, it is said to embody a codified constitution.
Constitutions concern different levels of sanghathan, isse sovereign rajya to companiyaan or unincorporated association.
A treaty which establishes an international organization is bhi iske samvidhan, in ki it hota define kaisaa ki sanghathan is gathit.
Within states, whether sovereign or federated, a constitution defines the siddhanth upon jisase the rajya is aadhaarit, the kaarividhi in jisase kanoon hai bana or by jisko.
Some constitutions, especially codified constitutions, bhi adhinium as limiters of rajya shakti, by establishing linon jisase a rajya 's shaskaon can nahin cross, such as fundamental rights.
George Washington at Constitutional sammelan of 1787, hastakshar of u.S. samvidhan.
The Constitution of India is the longest written constitution of any sovereign desh in the sansar, containing 448 aalekh, 12 schedules or 100 amendments, saath 117,369 shabd in iske angrezi bhashaa sanskaran, jabaki the sanyukt rajya samvidhan is the shortest written constitution, at 7 articles and 27 amendments.

Engineering management is a specialized form of prabandhan ki is chintit saath the anuprayog of abhiyantriki siddhanth to kaarobaar practice.
Engineering management is a career that brings saath the technological problem-solving savvy of abhiyantriki or the organizational, prashasnic, or niyojan abilities of prabandhan in order to oversee complex enterprises from conception to completion.
Example areas of abhiyantriki hai utpaada vikaas, nirmaan, nirmaan, dizine abhiyantriki, audyogic abhiyantriki, praudyogiki, utpaadan, or koi other field that employs personnel who perform an engineering function.
Successful engineering managers typically aavashyaktaa prashikshan or anubhav in kaarobaar or abhiyantriki.
Technically inept managers tend to be vanchit of support by unke takneekee toli, or non-commercial prabandhak tend to kami commercial acumen to deliver in a market economy.
Largely, engineering managers manage engineers who are driven by non-entrepreneurial thinking, yun aavashyaktaa the jaruri logon kaushal to coach, mentor or motivate takneekee peshewar.
abhiyantriki peshewar joining nirmaan companiyaan sometimes become engineering managers by default after a period of time.
They are required to learn how to manage ekbar ve hai on the job, haalanki is is usually an ineffective way to develop managerial abilities.
In an insurance policy, the deductible is the raashi of kharch ki jarur be sashulk out of jeb pehle an insurer will pay any expenses.
In general usage, the term deductible may be prayukt to describe ek of anek prakaar of clauses ( dekhie neeche ) ki hai prayukt by insurance companies as a threshold for policy payments.
Deductibles are typically used to deter the vishaal kramank of naganya daawa ki a upabhokta can be reasonably apekshit to bhaaluu the cost of.
By restricting its coverage to events that are significant enough to incur large costs, the insurance firm expects to adaa out thodaa choti amounts much kam aksar, rusht much ucchtar bachat.
As a result, bime premium hai typically sasta jab they involve higher deductibles.
Deductibles are normally provided as clauses in an bime niti ki dictate kaisaa much of an insurance-covered expense is borne by the policyholder.
They are normally quoted as a phixd maatra or is a bhaag of sabase nitiyon covering nuksaan to the niti holder.
The insurer then becomes liable for claimable kharch ki exceed is raashi ( vishay to the adhiktam sum claimable indicated in the contract ).
Depending on the niti, the deductible may lagu prati covered ghatana, or prati year.
For policies jahaan incidences hai nahin aasaan to delimit ( liye udhaaharan swasthya bime ), the deductible is typically applied per year.
Several deductibles can be niyat by the insurer aadhaarit on the cause of the claim.
For example, a single housing bime niti may contain anek deductible amounts liye ghaataa or kshati arising isse chori, aag, prakritik calamities, evacuation etc.
There are also deductible reimbursement kaarykram ki reimburse a deductible in the event of an swachaalit, ghar, boat/yacht or health insurance claim.
An invoice or bill is a commercial dastauez jari by a vikreta to a kharidaar, indicating the utpaada, quantities, or agreed prices for products or services the seller has provided the buyer.
An invoice indicates the bikri lenden tabhi.
bhugtan sharten hai swatantra of the invoice and are negotiated by the buyer and the seller.
bhugtan sharten hai praayah shaamil on the invoice.
The buyer could have already sashulk liye the utpaada or sevaayen listed on the invoice.
Buyer can also have a adhiktam kramank of dinon in jisase to adaa liye ye goods or is sometimes offered a discount if paid before the due date.
In the rental udyog, an chaalaan jarur shaamil a vishisht sandarbh to the avadhi of the samay hone billed, so in jod to maatra, daam or chhot the invoicing amount is also based on duration.
generally prayek lakeer of a rental chaalaan hoga refer to the vaastavik hours, days, weeks, months, etc., being billed.
From the point of drishy of a vikreta, an chaalaan is a bikri invoice.
isse the point of drishy of a buyer, an invoice is a purchase invoice.
The dastauez indicates the kharidaar or vikreta, lakin the pad chaalaan indicates money is owed or owing.
In English, the context of the pad chaalaan is praayah prayukt to clarify iske arth, aise as `` we bheja unhen an chaalaan '' ( ve owe us dhan ) or `` we praapt an chaalaan from them '' ( we owe them money ).
The right main bronchus ( or right primary bronchus, or right principal bronchus ) is a bronchus of the respiratory system.
It is wider, shorter, or adhik lambavat in disha than the left.
It is about 2.5 cm long, or enters the sahi fefdon nearly vipareet the paanchvaan thoracic vertebra.
The azygos vein arches over it isse peeche ; or the sahi pulmonary artery lies at first below and then in front of it.
About 2 cm from its commencement it detaa band a shakha to the apper pali of the sahi lung.
This is termed the eparterial shakha of the bronchus, kuki it arises upar the sahi pulmonary artery.
The bronchus now passes below the dhamni, or is gyaat as the hyparterial shakha ; it divides into do branches for the middle and lower lobes.
If a foreign body in the airway passes through the trachea, it will most sambhavit daalen the sahi pramukh bronchus bajaay of the baayein, due to the straighter sanrekhan of the sahi bronchus to the trachea.
Squash is a racquet sport nibhaai by do ( singles ) or chaar khilaadi ( yugal ) in a four-walled adaalat saath a choti, hollow rubber ball.
The khilaadi jarur vaikalpik in striking the ball saath unke racquet or hit the ball onto the playable surfaces of the four walls of the court.
The game was formerly called squash racquets, a sandarbh to the `` squashable '' naram ball prayukt in the khel ( compared saath the fatter ball used in its parent game racquets or rackets ).
squash is pahachaanaa by the ioc or samarthak hai lobbying liye its incorporation in a future Olympic program.
In 2003, forbs rated squash as the kramank ek healthiest sport to play.
Residual oil is aayal mila in kam ekaagratha naturally or in exhausted oil fields.
Often mixed with water, it can nahin be baraamad by conventional takneekon.
However, it can be recovered using carbon dioxide-enhanced aayal recovery ( co2 eor ) jisase involves injecting carbon dioxide into the khub reducing shyanta or badhanaa pravaah of the oil.
The technique is nahin nai lakin rai nahin maharoom prayukt extensively on avshesh aayal zones, low-grade jamaa of petroleum aise as the 38 vargakar miles in the Permian Basin of Texas leased by Elliott Roosevelt Jr.
The technique is limited by uplabdhta of carbon dioxide.
It does not result in sequestration of the carbon dioxide lakin the gas is recycled as much as possible.
United rajya reserves of avshesh aayal hai anumaanit to be 100 billion barrels.

The Great Chicago Fire was a conflagration ki burned isse sande, aktubar 8, to jaldi mangalvaar, aktubar 10, 1871, hatya sainkadon or destroying about in Chicago, Illinois.
Though the fire was one of the largest U.S. disasters of the 19th century, the rebuilding that began helped develop Chicago as ek of the sabase populous or economically mahatvapurn American cities.
Henry VIII ( 28 june 1491 – 28 janvari 1547 ) thi king of england from 21 April 1509 until his death.
He was lord, or baad king, of ireland, as khub as continuing the nammaatr arji by the angrezi monarchs to the Kingdom of France.
Henry was the second monarch of the Tudor dynasty, succeeding uske pita, henry saat.
Besides his six marriages, henry viii is gyaat liye uske bhoomika in the virah of the girijaghar of england from the Roman Catholic Church.
Henry 's struggles saath rome led to the virah of the girijaghar of england isse papal praadhikaar, the viched of the Monasteries, and his own establishment as the Supreme Head of the Church of England.
Yet he remained a believer in core Catholic theological teachings, bhi baad uske excommunication isse the roman catholic girijaghar.
Henry oversaw the vidhik sangh of england or wales saath the kanoon in Wales Acts 1535 and 1542.
In 1513, the new king allied with the Holy Roman Emperor, maximillian i, or invaded frans in 1513 saath a vishaal, well-equipped fouj, lakin hasil choti at a considerable vittiya cost.
Maximillian, for his part, used the English invasion to uske apana ends, or is prejudiced england 's kshamta to shikast the french.
This foray would prove the prarambh of an obsession liye henry, jo invaded again in 1544.
This time, Henry 's forces captured the important city of Boulogne, lakin again the paavan roman samraat, charles v, samarthit henry tabhi as long as he needed to or england, strained by the vishaal laagat of the yuddh, ransomed the nagar back for peace.
His contemporaries mana henry in uske pradhan to be an aakarshak, shikshit or sampannataa king, or he rai maharoom varnit as `` one of the most charismatic rulers to sit on the English throne ''.
Besides ruling saath nirpeksh shakti, he bhi sagaai khud as an author and composer.
His desire to provide England with a male heir – which stemmed partly from personal vanity and partly kuki he believed a beti hota be asamarth to consolidate the tuder rajvansh or the najuk salaam ki existed following the yudhon of the gulab – led to the two things for which Henry is most remembered : his six marriages and the English Reformation.
Henry became rugn mote or uske swasthya suffered, contributing to uske maut in 1547.
He is aksar characterised in uske baad jivan as a lustful, egotistical, harsh, and insecure king.
La Reina del Sur ( The Queen of the South ) is a Spanish-language telenovela utpaadit by the sanyukt rajya television sanjaal telemundo, in sangyojan saath the antena 3 network and RTI Producciones.
Based on a novel of the same name by Spanish author Arturo pérez-reverte, the naatak depicts the vruddhi of terresa mendosa ( ket del castillo ), a yang stri isse mexico jo becomes the sabase shaktishaalee drug trafficker in southern Spain.
Patricio Wills, the adhyaksh of telemundo television studios, thi the executive producer.
Though La Reina del Sur was nominated for Novela of the Year, pasandida sise abhinetri, or behtareen karaab lack video, it jiti no puraskaar.
With a $ 10 million budget, La Reina del sur thi the sabase mahangi telenovela kabhi utpaadit by Telemundo.
The program 's premiere on farvari 28, 2011, thi the sanjaal 's ucchtam rated premiere for a telenovela to date.
The kaarykram aksar varchasv iske samay slot, bhi over angrezi bhashaa programing on other major U.S. networks.
La Reina del Sur samaapt iske 63 apisod chalaaen on telemundo or iske 13 apisod chalaaen on Antena 3 simultaneously on May 30, 2011.
The final episode was the highest rated broadcast in telemundo 's 19-year itihaas ( 4.2 lakh darshak ), or taal sab of the angrezi bhashaa u.S. television sanjaal to earn the number one slot in the 18-49 adult demographic.
The program 's success spurred Telemundo to launch iske pehla abhiyaan to laabh the shrenee an emi puraskaar namakan.
A one-night special featuring several cast members aired on may 31, 2011, or chihnit the telemundo debyue of vikhyath latina television vyaktitv Cristina Saralegui.
la reina del sur is broadcast in anek anya bazaar, sahit srbija, colombia, chile, cyprus, nikaragua, costa rika, Mexico, Albania, Hungary, Slovenia, Croatia, Romania, ( among others ).

A web hosting service is a type of Internet hosting seva ki allows individuals or sanghathan to mek unke jalsthal accessible via the World Wide Web.
Web hosts are companies that provide space on a sarwar swaamitv or leased liye upyog by client, as khub as providing antarjaal connactivity, typically in a data center.
Web hosts can also provide data center space and connectivity to the Internet for other sarwar stith in unke aankada bich, pukaara colocation, bhi gyaat as awaas in latin america or France.
the paimaana of web hosting sevaayen varies greatly.
The most basic is web page and small-scale file hosting, where files can be uploaded via File transafar protocol ( apatpi ) or a web interfes.
The files are usually vitarit to the web `` as is '' or saath minimal prasanskaran.
Many antarjaal seva pradaataaon ( isps ) prastaav is seva free to subscribers.
Individuals and sanghathan may bhi obtain web pej hosting from alternative service providers.
Personal web site hosting is typically free, advertisement-sponsored, or inexpensive.
Business web site hosting praayah rai a ucchtar vyay depending upon the size and type of the website.
Single page hosting is generally sufficient liye nijee web pages.
A complex site calls for a more vyapak package ki provides database support or anuprayog vikaas plateform ( e.g. PHP, Java, Ruby on Rails, ColdFusion, or ASP.NET ).
These facilities allow customers to write or install scripts liye anuprayog jaise forums or saamagree prabandhan.
Also, surakshit sockets parat ( esasail ) is typically used for e-commerce.
The host may also provide an interface or control falak liye managing the web sarwar or installing script, as khub as anya maudul and service applications like e-mail.
Some hosts specialize in certain software or services ( e.g. e-commerce ), jisase hai commonly prayukt by larger companiyaan ki outsource sanjaal avasanrachana.
Madden NFL ( known as John Madden footbaal pehle 1993 ) is an amareeki footbaal video khel shrenee viksit by electronic Arts Tiburon for EA Sports.
The game series is named after Pro footbaal haul of famer jon maden, a well-known purv super katori –winning coach of the Oakland Raiders and color commentator.
The shrenee is the behtareen selling ea khel series.
The khel have consistently maharoom a behtareen vikreta, or rai even spawned TV shows where players compete.
Among the khel 's yathartwaadee suvidhaayen shaamil sophisticated playbooks or khilaadi aankde, or awaz commentary that allows players to hear the game as if it were a real TV broadcast.
The Madden enegel shrenee rai maharoom nicknamed the NFL 's 33rd Franchise.
The series was originally conceived by electronic kala sansthaapak trip hockins, jo tab approached maden in 1984 for his endorsement and expertise.
Due to maden 's insistence ki the khel be as yathartwaadee as sambhavit, the pehla sanskaran of John Madden Football was not released until 1988.
The second version of the game was released in 1990, saath salanaa sanskaran chunki tab.
The series ' naam thi badla to maden enegel in 1993 baad ea acquired the adhikaron to use NFL teams and players.
Despite Madden 's retirement as a broadcaster in 2009, he continues to lend uske naam or provide expertise for the game.

In law, a set-off is a statutory raksha to the puure or to a portion of a plaintiff 's claim.
It had no astitv antargat the angrezi aam vidhi, hone nirmit by 2 jeeyo. ii c. 22 liye the raahat of insolvent karjadaar, haalanki set-off was recognized in equity.
Such a defense could be pleaded tabhi in aadar of paraspar debts of a definite akshar, or kiya nahin lagu to maamle in jisase kshatipurti were claimed, nor to equitable claims or demands.
By the rules of the Supreme Court ( O. XIX. r. 3 ) a defendant in an action may set band or niyat up koi sahi or arji by rasta of counterclaim viruddh the daawa of a abhiyokta, or aise set-off or counterclaim has the same effect as a statement of claim in a cross-action.
